headline: ADP to Announce Third Quarter Fiscal 2025 Financial Results on April 30, 2025
summary: ADP (Nasdaq: ADP), a leading global provider of Human Capital Management (HCM) solutions, is scheduled to release its financial results for the third fiscal quarter ending March 31, 2025 before the opening of the Nasdaq on Wednesday, April 30, 2025.
